# Repository root — pointer to the canonical environment template
#
# The app loads environment from:
#   inventoryProjBrgy/inventoryProjBrgy/.env.local
#   inventoryProjBrgy/inventoryProjBrgy/.env
#
# Copy the template (placeholders only, no secrets committed):
#   inventoryProjBrgy/inventoryProjBrgy/.env.example
#   → inventoryProjBrgy/inventoryProjBrgy/.env.local
#
# Example (run from repo root):
#   copy inventoryProjBrgy\inventoryProjBrgy\.env.example inventoryProjBrgy\inventoryProjBrgy\.env.local
#
# Minimum to run API + DB: set DB_* and JWT_SECRET in .env.local (see template comments).
